        Gets all LogEntries from database fulfilling criteria specified by parameters
        Parameters:
        email - the email used to fetch logs, any if null
        type - the log type used to fetch logs, any if null
        startDate - the start Date to fetch logs from
        endDate - the end Date to fetch logs to
        ip - the ip used to fetch logs, any if null
        Returns:
        ArrayList containing all the LogEntrys in the database that match given parameters
